            "description": "At the International Olympic Committee (IOC), Olympic Broadcasting Services (OBS) and Olympic Channel Services (OCS), cyber security is high on the agenda. Michiel is as project manager responsible for the complete awareness & training project at all three organizations. \n\nThe awareness activities are risk-based and started with the creation of a security awareness strategy to define the risks, goals, learning objectives (desired knowledge, attitude and behaviour), awareness & communication methods and planning. Furthermore, Atos develops e-learning courses and delivers over 30 smaller awareness messages and activities (such as posters, factsheets, management commitment sessions and team meetings) to keep information security and cyber security on top of mind of the employees.",
            "contributors": [
